file.string: This application allows two Android devices to carry out two-way text chat over Bluetooth. It demonstrates all the fundamental Bluetooth API capabilites, such as: (1) Scanning for other Bluetooth devices (2) Querying the local Bluetooth adapter for paired Bluetooth devices (3) Establishing RFCOMM channels/sockets (4) Connecting to a remote device (5) Transfering data over Bluetooth
